title: Metallica - Live Shit Binge and Purge Mexico 1993
description:
Metallica performing at the Sports Palace, Mexico City, Mexico. Recorded over 5 days! February 25th, 26th, 27th, and March 1st, & 2nd, 1993.

Setlist:
00) The Ecstasy of Gold
01) Enter Sandman
02) Creeping Death
03) Harvester of Sorrow
04) Welcome Home (Sanitarium)
05) Sad But True
06) Of Wolf and Man
07) The Unforgiven
08) Justice Medley : Eye of the Beholder, Blackened, The Frayed Ends of Sanity, ...And Justice For All.
09) Solos (Bass & Guitar)
10) Through the Never
11) For Whom The Bell Tolls
12) Fade to Black
13) Master of Puppets
14) Seek and Destroy
15) Whiplash
16) Nothing Else Matters
17) Wherever I May Roam
18) Am I Evil?
19) Last Caress
20) One
21) So What? / Battery (Includes intros of Ride the Lightning, No Remorse)
22) The Four Horsemen
23) Motorbreath
24) Stone Cold Crazy

In my opinion, this ranks second to Seattle 89 in the Live Shit concerts. Pity, no video is available. But still, play it loud... :)
